Known issues in MAD-PMIPv6
------------------------

If you run into any of the issues below, don't bother reporting them
unless you can provide a fix, as we are already aware of them.

General issues
--------------

* MAD-PMIPv6 does not support IPsec

* PBUs and PBAs sequence numbers are not properly parsed hence some
  ordering mismatch might arise

* MARs do not track IP flows, hence MARs anchoring inactive flows
  will not be de-registered

* Number of MNs is limited to 16